data.description: 2 Bedroom 1 Bath Bungalow with a Full Basement and detached 1 Car Garage. Newer Kitchen with Granite countertops decorated back splash, SS appliances and oak cabinets. Updated first floor bath with a bidet toilet. Updated Light fixtures, Hardwood Floors throughout the first-floor bedrooms, kitchen, living room and dining room. Nice front porch deck leading to the enclosed front porch.  Full unfinished basement ready for your ideas, however there is a 5x10 workroom already there and a 5x11 storage area. The furnace/CA and Humidifier were updated in 2021. The electric has been updated, all doors have been updated to 6 panel white doors, most windows have been updated too. Long driveway has ample parking and two parking pads for turn around.
